 "name": "RPlog_Retribution_-_The_Empire_Wedges_In",
 "title": "Retribution: The Empire Wedges In",
 "summary": "Aboard the Imperial Star Destroyer Broadsword, Captain Caiton and Lt. Nelhrn review the battle plan for the fight over Coruscant, with Caiton highlighting the New Republic flagship Reprisal as the main target. Her officer Keline studies the screen and pledges to carry out her orders. As the Empire presses its advantage and wedges deeper into the Republic's defensive lines, the log captures the cold, methodical Imperial command coordinating the next phase of the battle of retribution.",
